annotation_set.note:
Note that a portion of the LRG does not map to the GRCh37 assembly.
This is due to a gap in GRCh37.p13 (NC_000002.11, from 3,529,313 to 3,579,313) which results in the 3'-end of the LRG/RefSeqGene being truncated by 1910-nt when aligned with this build. This gap was resolved in GRCh38 and the full LRG maps to that build.

annotation_set.comment: Annotation is based on Ensembl release 96 (GRCh38 primary assembly)
